title: The race may be long but you are stronger than you give yourself credit.

The view is beautiful from the top, but there is beauty in the climb. Don't overlook it.
Discipline will take you places where motivation can't.
You CAN, end of story.
Never stop dreaming.
You get tested the most when you're about to reach a new level, don't break.
Negativity is a choice. What are you choosing?
What we fear doing is usually what we need to do the most.
If you cannot do great things, do small things in a great way.

Trade your expectations for appreciation.

Don't let disappointment defeat you, let it drive you.
Delayed does not mean denied it just means you're gonna have to wait a little longer and work a little harder.

You already have what it takes.

Why not YOU?

Luck? No you make your own luck.

Life is a circle of happiness, sadness, hard times, and good times. If you are going through hard times, have faith that good times are on the way
